@node	SOURCE	"Source Code"

@{b}@{u}Source Code@{uu}@{ub}

The source code for RealDrag is provided. My intention is that someone
incorporate it into a larger Commodity, such as Yak, of MultiCX. That way you
get more for less overhead.
@{"                            Source Code                                    " link RealDrag.c/Main}

@endnode

